Youths of Maraban Kagoro, Kaura Local Government Area of Kaduna State, have mounted roadblocks to protest an attack on Agban, along Gidan Waya Road. Gunmen were said to have attacked the area on Sunday evening. The angry youths burned tires and attacked some passengers to protest the attack, killing two persons in Kafanchan. Schools and businesses are currently under lock and key for fear of being attacked. The Kaduna State Police Command spokesperson, ASP Muhammed Jalige, could not be reached for comments as calls to His phone were not answered.